<title>Ducktype 1.0</title>
<subtitle>A lightweight markup language for Mallard</subtitle>

<p style="lead">Ducktype is a lightweight markup language designed
explicitly for writing Mallard pages. This format is influenced by
lightweight formats like Markdown, AsciiDoc, and RST. But it is
designed to allow nearly everything that can be done with Mallard
XML, including semantic markup, automatic linking, well-defined
nesting, and embedding extensions and other formats.</p>

